OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fday with a few light showers about,
OL,7,Fbut these should die away by late
OL,8,Fmorning with brighter spells building
OL,9,Finto the dry afternoon. Northerly
OL,10,Fwinds initially strong across Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOrkney staying dry through
OL,13,Fthe day, but a few light well
OL,14,Fscattered showers affecting Shetland.
OL,15,FSome late sunshine then clear spells.
OL,16,FNortherly winds fresh across Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
