OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAnother generally fair days
OL,6,Fweather in prospect with most dry with
OL,7,Foccasional brighter spells developing.
OL,8,FWinds northeasterly and relatively
OL,9,Flight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,12,Fchange to more unsettled conditions
OL,13,Fwith a series of rain bands crossing
OL,14,Ffrom the south. However, with winds
OL,15,Fstaying southwesterly temperatures a
OL,16,Flittle up on the seasonal averages.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
